# Search firewall (LAB-DOC-SEARCH-FIREWALL-P1)
# Keeps default ripgrep / Grep-tool results off stale + noise paths so agents
# don't drift. Nothing is deleted — excluded from DEFAULT search only.
# To search everything: `rg --no-ignore <pattern>`. See SEARCH.md.

# --- Build artifacts (pure noise, code + doc search) ---
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.svelte-kit/

# --- Superseded docs (content migrated, SUPERSEDED banner present) ---
# These caused real "stale claim outranks live code" drift. Excluded from default
# search; the live answer is the crate IMPLEMENTED_SURFACE.md + the gov ledger.
lab-docs/igniter-delta-1.md

# --- Future: the lab-docs staleness sweep moves dead docs here, then uncomment ---
# lab-docs/archive/

# NOTE: .agents/** is a hidden (dot) dir → already invisible to default ripgrep
# (needs --hidden). The card / portfolio-index / operational-archive noise lives
# there and therefore needs NO exclusion here. The searchable stale surface is
# lab-docs/**, which is evidence — do NOT blanket-exclude it; the verify-first
# rule (SEARCH.md) is what neutralizes it. Add only specific superseded files.
